* * Set * * An ASN1 type for an Set, that extends a Sequence * Copyright (c) 2007 Henri Torgemane * * See LICENSE.txt for full license information.

 
package com.hurlant.util.der
{
  public dynamic class Set extends Sequence implements IAsn1Type
  {
    public function Set(type:uint = 0x31, length:uint = 0x00) {
      super(type, length);
    }


    public override function toString():String {
      var s:String = DER.indent;
      DER.indent += "    ";
      var t:String = join("\n");
      DER.indent= s;
      return DER.indent+"Set["+type+"]["+len+"][\n"+t+"\n"+s+"]";
    }
    
  }
}
